DescPackaging: >>
We store the ls-R files of the texmf trees in %p/etc/ls-R/ because they will 
 change after installation.  Other packages should use %p/bin/mktexlsr 
 (not texhash) to update these, and they should take care to update in
 a PostRmScript as well if they have modified these files during or after 
 installation.
<<
